---
import { C, FONT } from "../infographicTokens";
---

<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 720 280" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
  <title>Why you cannot bill every paid hour</title>
  <desc>
    A technician is paid for a full 8-hour day but only about 5 to 5.5 hours are billable. Drive time,
    paperwork, restocking, and travel between jobs are paid but not billed, so the billable rate must
    recover the cost of the whole day.
  </desc>

  <rect x="8" y="8" width="704" height="264" rx="12" fill={C.panelBg} stroke={C.border} />
  <text x="24" y="36" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="14" font-weight="700">You pay 8 hours, you bill ~5</text>
  <text x="24" y="56" fill={C.muted} font-family={FONT} font-size="11">A paid 8-hour day rarely yields 8 billable hours — ~65% is typical</text>

  <!-- full day bar -->
  <text x="24" y="92" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11.5" font-weight="700">Paid day</text>
  <rect x="120" y="76" width="560" height="30" rx="6" fill={C.blueLight} stroke={C.blue} stroke-width="1.3" />
  <text x="400" y="96" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.blue} font-family={FONT} font-size="11.5" font-weight="800">8.0 paid hours</text>

  <!-- billable portion -->
  <text x="24" y="142" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11.5" font-weight="700">Billable</text>
  <rect x="120" y="126" width="364" height="30" rx="6" fill={C.primaryLight} stroke={C.primary} stroke-width="1.3" />
  <text x="302" y="146" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.primary} font-family={FONT} font-size="11.5" font-weight="800">~5.2 billable hours</text>
  <!-- non-billable portion -->
  <rect x="488" y="126" width="192" height="30" rx="6" fill={C.orangeLight} stroke={C.orange} stroke-width="1.3" />
  <text x="584" y="146" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.orange} font-family={FONT} font-size="10.5" font-weight="800">2.8 non-billable</text>

  <rect x="120" y="178" width="560" height="74" rx="10" fill={C.white} stroke={C.border} />
  <text x="136" y="200" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="700">Paid but not billed:</text>
  <text x="136" y="220" fill={C.muted} font-family={FONT} font-size="10.5">Drive time · restocking the truck · paperwork &amp; photos · callbacks · waiting on parts</text>
  <text x="136" y="240" fill={C.muted} font-family={FONT} font-size="10.5">Divide true hourly cost by the billable fraction (≈0.65) to recover the whole day.</text>
</svg>
